responses: {"Q0":"This was horrible. Instead of having keys on home row where it'd be natural, making us scrunch up our hands for the number keys was beyond suboptimal.  I really have to wonder if the person who put this together actually went through it. Do you have some type of abnormal fingers, where it's not uncomfortable to put it in that position?  If you care about your data, you should know that your results are skewed because of the inane keyboard input choice.  Suggestion: Use S D F and J K L, or at least allow that as an option. Geez. Were it not for hitting the wrong key half the time, my bonus would be much higher."}
